data.description: Opportunity for qualifying buyers to assume sellers 2.5% FHA. Four bedroom, three full bath, all brick home in Stewarts Creek school zone. Convenient to shopping, and commuting. Minutes to I24 and I840; only 30 mins to Nashville airport. Large, fenced yard that backs up to a tree lined 5 acre lot to the rear. Beautiful landscaping, nice outdoor areas, gazebo remains. Easy walk to the pool.  Amazing, quiet neighborhood close to everything.
